Data.name: COCDefectsInTestPlan BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('COCTestExecsInTestPlan BE') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: COCTestExecsInTestPlan BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testPlanTestExecutions('COCTestPlan BE') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleased BE
Data.jql: filter = 425948 AND (fixVersion in unreleasedVersions() OR fixVersion is EMPTY)

Data.name: COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleasedAssignedToCurrentUser BE
Data.jql: filter = 425948 AND issue in testExecWithTestRunsAssignedToUser() AND (fixVersion in unreleasedVersions() OR fixVersion is EMPTY)

Data.name: COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleasedPASSEvidence BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testTestExecutions('COCTestsInTestPlanUnreleasedPASSEvidence BE', PASS)

Data.name: COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleasedPASSNoEvidence BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testTestExecutions('COCTestsInTestPlanUnreleasedPASSNoEvidence BE', PASS)

Data.name: COCTestsInTestPlan BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('COCTestExecsInTestPlan BE') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: COCTestsInTestPlanUnreleased BE
Data.jql: filter = 425953 AND (fixVersion in unreleasedVersions() OR fixVersion is EMPTY)

Data.name: COCTestsInTestPlanUnreleasedAssignedToCurrentUserPASSNoEvidence BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND (issue in testExecutionTests('COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleasedAssignedToCurrentUser BE', PASS, '', 'true', '', '', 'false') OR issue in testExecutionTests('COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleasedAssignedToCurrentUser BE', PASS, '', 'false', '', '', 'false'))

Data.name: COCTestsInTestPlanUnreleasedPASSEvidence BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND (issue in testExecutionTests('COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleased BE', PASS, '', 'true', '', '', 'true') OR issue in testExecutionTests('COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleased BE', PASS, '', 'false', '', '', 'true'))

Data.name: COCTestsInTestPlanUnreleasedPASSNoEvidence BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND (issue in testExecutionTests('COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleased BE', PASS, '', 'true', '', '', 'false') OR issue in testExecutionTests('COCTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleased BE', PASS, '', 'false', '', '', 'false'))
